23
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,000
Vandan jî gundê Habû ne.
 
This side is the village of Habû.

24
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,000
Û zeytûn jî îsal îyanî...
 
And the olives this year are, you know...

25
