Gundê Habû, korê çûlê.
 
Habû village, deeper in the countryside.

66
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,000
Kûlê çûlê, û darra bûn.
 
Deeper in the countryside, and there were trees.

67
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,000
