184
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:57,000
Gam kuta çûne... çûne... noko me ştarol duser Kaniya
Berbîra, Berberxa, Berkara... gi fikrê me damayî.
 
When we went... went... now we have wandered to Kaniya
